description: A woman visiting from Northern Ireland is jailed after catching a bus, breaching quarantine rules.
title: Isle of Man visitor jailed after bus journey to locksmith during quarantine
title_page: Isle of Man visitor jailed after bus journey to locksmith during quarantine - BBC News
maintext: She also wanted advice on how to open a safe which was thought to contain documents that could help to get the probate of her mother's will "resolved" two years after her death.
